(2, 1, '2018-11-27 01:44:06', '2018-11-27 01:44:06', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="stm-col-pad-right"][vc_single_image image="518" img_size="large" stm_fancybox="yes" css=".vc_custom_1544323332567{margin-bottom: 35px !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style="margin-bottom: 18px;">WELCOME TO<span style="color: #f0c540;">MOVIE STAR MOTORS</span></h3>\r\n<h5 style="margin-bottom: 22px;">Before we get ahead of ourselves, we want to welcome you to Movie Star Motors.</h5>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 26px;">We appreciate you taking the time today to visit our web site. Our goal is for you to be able to conveniently find vehicles for your movie, video, photography production or special event. The search for the perfect cars, airplanes, or boats for a scene can be long and tedious. Let us do all of the research while you continue to produce your masterpiece.</p>\r\n<span style="color: #888888;"><em> LINO ROSADO, President of Movie Star Motors</em></span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1544325370262{margin-top: 5px !important;padding-bottom: 23px !important;}" el_class="stm-col-pad-right"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1544323400301{margin-bottom: 23px !important;}"]\r\n<h3>ABOUT US</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The idea for Movie Star Motors started when the father of our CEO had his car cast for the movie A Bronx Tale back in 1993. Star struck by the entire experience in 2008 he realized that there was a need for media productions that wasnt being supported properly. Movie and television productions, as well as advertising and photography projects large and small were always going to be in need of all types of vehicles. Movie Star Motors was going to be there to supply them all!\r\n\r\nMovie Star Motors represents and casts all kinds of vehicles such as cars, airplanes, boats, helicopters, construction and military vehicles, for many types of productions. We help cast new vehicles and old; pristine and rust buckets; if there is a vehicle that is needed we reach out to every day vehicle owners to fulfill that need.\r\n\r\nIf you always wanted a vehicle of yours in a movie or if you have a production of your own that needs vehicles, let Movie Star Motors help make that dream come true![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="505" img_size="large" alignment="center" stm_fancybox="yes"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1544325251831{background-color: #000000 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="IF IT ROLLS, FLOATS OR FLIES WE''RE THERE FOR YOU!" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff"][stm_color_separator][stm_carousel slides_per_row="6" images="532,524,531,530,529,528"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about_us', '', '', '2018-12-09 03:21:55', '2018-12-09 03:21:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/msm/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
