emorable one. Let Movie Star Motors find the vehicles you need so you can create the perfect scene.</span>[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-rental-medal_rent" title="Expand Your Business" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1548030061175{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Have a fleet of trucks, construction vehicles, or other equipment for rent? Partner with us and see what we can do for your bottom line.</span></p>\r\n[/stm_icon_box][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-like_it" title="Easy Payments" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1548030070972{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Movie Star Motors is dedicated to making sure that payments are quick and easy. Whether you''re the car owner or the producer of the production, we know your time is valuable.</span></p>\r\n[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-icon-add_car" title="Hire Vehicles" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1548030081446{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #000000;">Hire vehicles for your production. We are your one stop shop for all of the vehicles you need to make your project come to life.</span></p>\r\n[/stm_icon_box][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-phone" title="Customer Support" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1548030091100{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;"><span style="color: #000000;">We''re here to answer any questions that you might have and work with you through every step of the process. Call us before, during or after production. We want to make sure that the experience is enjoyable for everyone involved.</span></p>\r\n[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="stm-fullwidth-with-parallax" css=".vc_custom_1548024035108{margin-bottom: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 51px !important;background-image: url(http://localhost/msm/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Classic-Cars-Lineup-1.jpg?id=505) !important;}"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="MAKE YOUR CAR A MOVIE STAR!" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:50px|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff|line_height:60px" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1548033585052{margin-top: 68px !important;margin-bottom: 51px !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row disable_element="yes"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="WHAT OUR CLIENTS SAY" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:30px|text_align:center|color:%23273f44|line_height:50px" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1484196997291{margin-bottom: 18px !important;}"][stm_testimonials slides_per_row="3"][stm_testimonial image_size="67x67" image="463,463,463,463" author="Ann Black"]Sed malesuada, neque quis tincidunt suscipit, lorem lectus rutrum lacus, a iaculis ipsum eros sed ipsum. Sed scelerisque massa ut nibh tincidunt, eget pellentesque.[/stm_testimonial][stm_tes