 vehicles and old; pristine and rust buckets; if there is a vehicle that is needed we reach out to every day vehicle owners to fulfill that need.\r\n\r\nIf you always wanted a vehicle of yours in a movie or if you have a production of your own that needs vehicles, let Movie Star Motors help make that dream come true![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="505" img_size="large" alignment="center" stm_fancybox="yes"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1544325251831{background-color: #000000 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="IF IT ROLLS, FLOATS OR FLIES WE''RE THERE FOR YOU!" font_container="tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff"][stm_color_separator][stm_carousel slides_per_row="6" images="532,524,531,530,529,528"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-12-09 03:19:41', '2018-12-09 03:19:41', '', 2, 'http://localhost/msm/2-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
