(2145, 1, '2019-01-14 01:51:58', '2019-01-14 01:51:58', '<p>[vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css_animation="flipInY" css=".vc_custom_1545003518737{margin-top: 75px !important;padding-top: 36px !important;padding-bottom: 500px !important;background: #ffffff url(http://localhost/msm/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/MSMLogoClearBack-2.jpg?id=625) !important;}" el_class="stm-background-centered"][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1484196732635{margin-bottom: 47px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text="WHY CHOOSE US" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:30px|text_align:center|color:%23273f44|line_height:50px" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1484196241978{margin-bottom: 53px !important;}"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-cash_dollar" title="Rent Your Vehicle" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1543368890669{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]</p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;">Make money renting your boat, plane or car. Let us make the connections while you have fun and reap the rewards.</p>\r\n<p>[/stm_icon_box][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-shield-o" title="Quality Research" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1543369128800{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]Our dedicated researchers are here to find what you are looking for to make your production a memorable one. Let Movie Star Motors find the vehicles you need so you can create the perfect scene.[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-rental-medal_rent" title="Expand Your Business" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1543368563934{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]</p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;">Have a fleet of trucks, construction vehicles, or other equipment for rent? Partner with us and see what we can do for your bottom line.</p>\r\n<p>[/stm_icon_box][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-like_it" title="Easy Payments" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1543369612659{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]</p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;">Movie Star Motors is dedicated to making sure that payments are quick and easy. Whether you''re the car owner or the producer of the production, we know your time is valuable.</p>\r\n<p>[/stm_icon_box][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-icon-add_car" title="Hire Vehicles" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff" css=".vc_custom_1543368625561{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}" icon_size="31" box_text_color="#888888" box_text_color_hover="#6e6e6e" line_height="20"]</p>\r\n<p style="line-height: 20px;">Hire vehicles for your production. We are your one stop shop for all of the vehicles you need to make your project come to life.</p>\r\n<p>[/stm_icon_box][stm_icon_box title_holder="h4" icon="stm-service-icon-phone" title="Customer Support" icon_bg_color="#f0c540" icon_color="#ffffff" box_bg_color="#ffffff"